INSERT INTO osyl2_syllabuselementattribute(ELEMENT_ID,NAME,VALUE) VALUES ('20011', 'text', '<div>You have two choices for the team project</div>\r\n                            <div>\r\n                              <ol>\r\n                                <li>HEC Montreal plans to introduce more and more fully online classes in the near future. One of the major problem with online classes is ensuring the integrity of the exam process. Obviously one way would be to ask students to come to a testing center. However, this approach is not very practical if we have students from many different countries. The School thus has asked me to find a technological solution to this problem. A number of companies claim to be able to solve this problem:</li>\r\n                                <ul>\r\n                                  <li>Software Secure</li>\r\n                                  <li>Respondus</li>\r\n                                  <li>Tegrity</li>\r\n                                  <li>ProctorU</li>\r\n                                  <li>Kryterion<br>\r\n                                    <span style=\"white-space: pre;\">\r\nWhat approach should I propose to the School?\r\n\r\n</span>\r\n                                  </li>\r\n                                </ul>\r\n                                <li>Choose asoftware product which is\r\ntargeted to and used by small-to-medium sized organizations. Your report should provide a complete picture of the product.</li>\r\n                              </ol>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                            <div>\r\n                              <br>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                              <div>Usually software is evaluated according to functional and non-functional attributes (see attached slides). However feel free to be creative.</div>\r\n                              <div>\r\n                                <br>\r\n                              </div>\r\n                                <div>The evaluation criteria are provided in the attached document.</div>');
